metadata.name: A New Terrain
metadata.description:
With the advancement of modern technology and the deterioration of our planet, humanity will find itself in need of finding a new home. As someone who loves space travel, the idea of exploring the unknown  makes me hopeful for our future.  I wanted this image to feel like it was a first visitor on a new planet, a new terrain. 

Shot in Joshua Tree, CA. 

1/1 image

Shot on 35mm by Alister Mori
